<i>adjective</i>: 우세스럽다 [우세스럽따], 욕되다 [욕뙤다/욕뛔다], 수치스럽다 [수치스럽따], 불미하다 [불미하다], 불명예스럽다 [불명예스럽따], 망신스럽다 [망신스럽따], 낯부끄럽다 [낟뿌끄럽따], 괘씸하다 [괘씸하다] <i>determiner</i>: 치욕적 [치욕쩍] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>우세스럽다 [우세스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>disgraceful; embarrassing</dd><br>
<dd>남에게서 놀림과 비웃음을 받을 만큼 창피한 데가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>So shameful as to cause teasing and ridicule from others.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>욕되다 [욕뙤다/욕뛔다]</dt><br>
<dd>disgraceful</dd><br>
<dd>부끄럽고 불명예스럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Shameful and dishonorable.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>수치스럽다 [수치스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>disgraceful; ignoble</dd><br>
<dd>매우 창피하고 부끄럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Extremely shameful and embarrassing.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>불미하다 [불미하다]</dt><br>
<dd>unsavory; scandalous; disgraceful</dd><br>
<dd>보기에 옳지 못하거나 떳떳하지 못하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Seeming unjust or dishonest.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>불명예스럽다 [불명예스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>dishonorable; disgraceful</dd><br>
<dd>사람들로부터 높은 평가나 좋은 평판을 받지 못하는 데가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Getting a bad reputation or losing people's respect.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>망신스럽다 [망신스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>disgraceful; shameful</dd><br>
<dd>망신을 당해 부끄럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling ashamed after suffering disgrace.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>낯부끄럽다 [낟뿌끄럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>shameful; disgraceful</dd><br>
<dd>창피하여 얼굴을 보이기가 부끄럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Causing embarrassment with shame.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>괘씸하다 [괘씸하다]</dt><br>
<dd>disgraceful; shameful</dd><br>
<dd>기대나 믿음에 어긋나는 못마땅한 행동을 하여 밉살스럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being hated for doing things that go against the expectations or trust of others.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>determiner</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>치욕적 [치욕쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>humiliating; disgraceful</dd><br>
<dd>욕되고 창피스러운.</dd><br>
<dd>Being dishonorable and shameful.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>